-- Obama Vows to `Spare No Effort' on Afghan Shootings
-- B y
-- 2012-03-13T16:23:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/obama-vows-to-spare-no-effort-on-afghan-shootings.html
President  Barack Obama  promised to 
“spare no effort” to fully investigate the killings of at 
least 16 Afghan civilians, allegedly at the hands of a U.S. 
Army staff sergeant. He speaks at The White House.  (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running Time: 01:55
 